tissue_diff = {}
concat_df = pd.DataFrame()
z_concat = pd.DataFrame()
gene_ls = {}
for tissue in tissues:
    t1 = df_concat[df_concat["sample"].str.contains(tissue)].drop_duplicates(["chr","start"])
    gene_ls[tissue] = t1.drop_duplicates("geneID").shape[0]
    t2 = nanopore_tpm[[tissue]]
    t2 = np.log10(t2[t2[tissue] >1])
    tissue_diff[tissue] = t1.shape[0]
    t2["type"] = t2.index.isin(t1["transID"])
#     t2["type"].value_counts()
    t2 = t2.reset_index()
# t2[t2["#feature_id"].str.startswith("trans")]
    t2 = t2[t2["transcript_name"].str.startswith("ENST")]
    t2["tissue"] = tissue
    t2.columns = ["ID","tpm","type","tissues"]
    concat_df = pd.concat([concat_df,t2],axis=0)
    z1 = t1.value_counts('type').to_frame()
    z1.columns = [tissue]
    z_concat = z1.join(z_concat)
    print(t1.shape,tissue)

        return "constitutive"

def myfun2(x):
    if (x["m6A"]==True) & (x["m5C"]==True) :
        return "Both"
    elif (x["m6A"]==False) & (x["m5C"]==False) :
        return "None"
    elif  (x["m6A"]==True) & (x["m5C"]==False) :
        return "m6A"
    else :
        return "m5C"
